1 86.353. The right of any person to a benefit, any
2 other right accrued or accruing to any person under the
3 provisions of sections 86.200 to 86.366 and the moneys
4 created pursuant to sections 86.200 to 86.366 are not
5 subject to execution, garnishment, attachment or any other
6 process whatsoever and are unassignable except as in
7 sections 86.200 to 86.366 specifically provided.
8 Notwithstanding the foregoing, nothing in this section shall
