79 franchise tax credit created pursuant to section 148.030,
80 the bank tax credit for S corporations created pursuant to

SB 889 21
81 section 143.471, the exam fee tax credit created pursuant to
82 section 148.400, the health insurance pool tax credit
83 created pursuant to section 376.975, the life and health
84 insurance guaranty tax credit created pursuant to section
85 376.745, the property and casualty guaranty tax credit
86 created pursuant to section 375.774, and the self-employed
