50 (2) As used in subsections [5 to 9] 1 to 5 of this
51 section, the following terms mean:
52 (a) "Accessible assistive technology device", an
53 assistive technology device, as defined in 20 U.S.C. Section
54 1401, as amended, that provides blind or visually impaired
55 students the benefits of an educational program in an
56 equally effective and integrated manner as that provided to
