101 the number required, the qualified company or qualified
102 military project shall not receive tax credits or retain the
103 withholding tax for the balance of the project period. If a

SB 889 131
104 statewide state of emergency exists for more than sixteen
105 months, a qualified company or industrial development
106 authority shall be entitled to a one-time suspension of
107 program deadlines equal to the number of months such
108 statewide state of emergency existed with any partial month
