251 applicable credit allowance date.
252 7. Under section 23.253 of the Missouri
253 sunset act:
254 (1) The provisions of the new program
255 authorized under this section shall
256 automatically sunset six years after September
257 4, 2007, unless reauthorized by an act of the
258 general assembly; and
259 (2) If such program is reauthorized, the
