93 secondary education shall:
94 (1) Train the teachers and administrators
95 of the five schools chosen for the pilot program
96 regarding the trauma-informed approach and how
97 to become trauma-informed schools;
98 (2) Provide the five schools with funds to
99 implement the trauma-informed approach; and
100 (3) Closely monitor the progress of the
101 five schools in becoming trauma-informed schools
102 and provide further assistance if necessary.
