19 and insurance as soon as practically possible.
20 2. The Missouri electronic prior
21 authorization committee shall consist of the
22 following members:
23 (1) Two members of the senate, appointed
24 by the president pro tempore of the senate;

SB 889 291
25 (2) Two members of the house of
26 representatives, appointed by the speaker of the
27 house of representatives;
